#. type: Plain text
#: /home/jb/Projects/Simon/content/pages/administrator/torhiddenservice.md:12
msgid ""
"### Configuring our hidden service Edit `/etc/tor/torrc`, and add these "
"lines:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/jb/Projects/Simon/content/pages/administrator/torhiddenservice.md:18
msgid ""
"```bash HiddenServiceDir /var/lib/tor/hidden_service/ HiddenServicePort 80 "
"127.0.0.1:80 HiddenServicePort 443 127.0.0.1:443 ```"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/jb/Projects/Simon/content/pages/administrator/torhiddenservice.md:23
msgid "### Restart Tor ```bash service tor restart ```"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/jb/Projects/Simon/content/pages/administrator/torhiddenservice.md:28
msgid ""
"### Get your Tor Hidden Service hostname ```bash cat "
"/var/lib/tor/hidden_service/hostname ```"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
