msgid ""
"### Avoid SSO redirection (optional)  If you want to avoid being redirected "
"to the SSO portal at login, you can deactivate SSOwat for this specific tor "
"domain, by editing the file `/etc/nginx/conf.d/random123456789.onion.conf` "
"and commenting the following line (two times):"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: /home/jb/Projects/Simon/content/pages/administrator/torhiddenservice.md:42
msgid "```bash #access_by_lua_file /usr/share/ssowat/access.lua; ```"
msgstr ""

